      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Mauston, Wisconsin, 1 August 1952",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "Mr. J. Edgar Hoover, Director",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "FBI",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "Washington, D. C.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "Dear Sir:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "As a retired member of the St Paul Police Force and having had",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "numerous pleasant contacts with Agent [REDACTED] and [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "I take the liberty of an opinion that came to me that the flying",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "saucers really seem possible that the released energy of exploded",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "Atomic bombs could be soaring around in the atmosphere. I know",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "you can channel this thought to the proper authorities and cer-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "tainly would appreciate your comments on this thought.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "I am a Veteran of both World War #1 and #2 and also a member of",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "the American Legion for 32 years. I am presently a member of",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "The American Legion Post #81 of Mauston, Wisconsin which is",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "known as the Darlen-Hoppe Post.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "If this thought is instrumental in tracking down the source of",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "this power thereby relieving some of the tension to our American",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "Country, it would be worth following up at this time.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "Thanking you very much for your cooperation and consideration in",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "this matter and will you please acknowledge and advise your com-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "ments.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "Yours very truly,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
